channel.title: Right i can spawn stuff i think, but i dont know how to actually get it in m inv
channel.description:
[b][/b] :cool: This is really annoying me now. Ive been trying to spawn weapons and i know for example you put:
::item 1234 100 <----------is that right?
And for money:
::pickup 0995 1000000 <--------is that right?
If yes where do i type these commands???
Please help me ! :eek:

item.title: Right i can spawn stuff i think, but i dont know how to actually get it in m inv
item.dc:creator: @Evil_Webster Evil Webster
item.description:
@Evil_Webster wrote:

just in the chat box, most servers disable spawning for average players, but if you have moparscape, use that, you can download it using the link at the top of the screen. Install it, run it, download the cache. Then click ‘start server’ then log in with any username or password, making sure the server name is ‘127.0.0.1’ and try to spawn there. your commands are fine. ::pickup 0995 999 will pick up 999gp.

Hope I Helped,
Evil
